Subscribe for more GTLive action! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 
Would You Rather - StankPat BEGINS! ►► http://bit.ly/1YEPbkj
Star Wars Battlefront & Darth MatPat's Lies! ►► http://bit.ly/1YEPdIZ

Enough of REGULAR Mario, I want a CHALLENGE! Today I tackled Cat Mario...and it's crazy controls...and it's TOO effective mushrooms, and TOTALLY MISLEADING stars and DEATH SPRINGS and IMMORTAL goombahs?! It's intense, it's weird, it's Cat Mario! Watch me claw my way through this classic Nintendo knock-off.
